est yet organised.  <P>Dr Stone said the scientists would also be checking the penguins' stress levels.  <P>\"We are prepared to watch them flap around and fall over as helicopters go over,\" he said. \"The penguins also tend to shake their heads and flap their flippers. If something disturbs them enough they move away or even start running.\"  <P>The survey will focus on the island's population of king penguins, the second biggest penguin in the world, weighing 35kg and a metre in height.  <P>The team will return for a further five weeks next winter to conduct trials monitoring the penguins' responses to flights by fixed-wing aircraft. <P><B>Useful links</B> <BR> <A HREF=\"http://www.falklands-nature.demon.co.uk/penguins/penguins.html\" TARGET=\"_NEW\">Falklands conservation penguins page</A><BR><A HREF=\"http://what-now.org/penguins.html\" TARGET=\"_NEW\">Penguins: the greatest animal on earth</A><BR><A HREF=\"http://home.capu.net/~kwelch/pp/species/king.html\" TARGET=\"_NEW\">The King penguin: multimedia site</A><BR><A HREF=\"http://home.capu.net/~kwelch/pp/species/rockhopper.html\" TARGET=\"_NEW\">The Rockhopper penguin: multimedia site</A><BR><A HREF=\"http://ourworld.compuserve.com/homepages/Peter_and_Barbara_Barham/pengies.htm\" TARGET=\"_NEW\">Pete and Barb's penguin pages: everything you want to know about penguins</A><BR><A HREF=\"http://www.ai.mit.edu/people/paulfitz/plank/horde.doit\" TARGET=\"_NEW\">Game - rampaging penguins</A><BR><A HREF=\"http://members.aol.com/darlingal9/ritz.html\" TARGET=\"_NEW\">Dancing penguins</A><BR><A HREF=\"http://www.snopes.com/critters/wild/penguin.htm\">Urban legends reference pages</A>","headline":"Navy to help with tottering penguins","trailText":"For years the mystery of the wobbling South Atlantic penguins has puzzled scientists and ornithologists alike. As military helicopters and planes fly overhead, the transfixed birds lean further and further back until they topple over. ","newspaperPageNumber":"4","shouldHideAdv